{"tid":1379091,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋班暴徒唔好再搞亂香港得唔得？","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T18:41:37.000Z","uid":146865,"like":8,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"81b22a16ef01f5309bf89f44127840679ac56300","tid":1379091,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:35:50.000Z","msg":"唔好意思啊呃你哋入嚟<br />\n我作為前線手足有幾樣嘢想檢討下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>第一<br />\n最前排一定要有豬嘴同眼罩（眼罩要密封唔好比煙入到去），因為裝備真係好重要，冇豬嘴同眼罩根本狠冇可能頂到啲催淚彈，一射完催淚彈同出速龍就勁混亂，加上啲裝備唔夠嘅手足煙入眼同鼻，令佢哋打唔開眼甚至行唔到，搞到人踩人，所以冇裝備唔好上前線，咁樣只會拖累到啲手足，最後搞到手足比人拉曬，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>第二<br />\n我覺得勇武手足要進化，因為咁多次嘅經驗同我講只守唔攻唔係辦法，好多時set曬防線，都淨係喺原地度等，比曬啲時間狗增援，所以我建議可以喺我哋人多嘅時候亦佢哋人手不足嘅時候攻上去，用人海戰術，前排一定要有盾陣用嚟擋橡膠子彈、海綿彈，我哋有人多嘅優勢，一定可以打殘戰啲狗同搶佢哋啲gear，不過呢一點要有大量勇武手足同齊裝先做得到。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>第三<br />\n我哋可以set一啲陷阱比啲狗，例如攞水喉射濕塊地、撤退嘅時候掉波子，咁樣拎啲狗唔會咁快就衝到過嚟，咁樣可以保障到前線嘅手足，而且set鐵馬同擺雜物嗰阻擋效果唔係太理想（set嘅時間好長）。<br />\n呢幾點喺我暫時諗到，希望各位可以補充或者交流下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79793e3dc247c90f453d9c933f40d201683d226f","tid":1379091,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:36:34.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"d00ac716ff1a2371f7dbc6799cf8a0dc87bc382d","tid":1379091,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:36:44.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"952b75757687f056b849ceff30a256db8e5f2577","tid":1379091,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"1e41ddc2a521d12cac0858d22f4ebfe57a0ca5b6","tid":1379091,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:20.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"5bda64d493a8c179c2c47b14925dc8e970391d64","tid":1379091,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:37:58.000Z","msg":"727 728 打人合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6N677ZNEHyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6N677ZNEHyo&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=e12abc48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6N677ZNEHyo</a>"},{"pid":"5fdaf3cbb512f806f78aa743166c516603d02aa5","tid":1379091,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b49b80d465e5ec4b12a2f168c98a3b607cca588","tid":1379091,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:12.000Z","msg":"唔好負評啦，睇下先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcad67d6132fc21d1bb6c38ba3de5357e8b4be4e","tid":1379091,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:33.000Z","msg":"幫手推！我無嘢講"},{"pid":"3142d94b4d2e9a600a18c9ef5d94c5dcae617e90","tid":1379091,"uid":41853,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"標題黨真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"7964f3b534b1e5bcbfda999f366711ed7436172b","tid":1379091,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3142d94b4d2e9a600a18c9ef5d94c5dcae617e90","tid":1379091,"uid":41853,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"標題黨真係好撚煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:39:38.000Z","msg":"想大家入嚟睇下，真係好重要"},{"pid":"8bfcdf4f78d7e0e11e67bf16dc46b721b7c04cbd","tid":1379091,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:40:20.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"eb6fd75153bb65e0d0d52406f9bd84550c88d31e","tid":1379091,"uid":146865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:40:30.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"aa57958dd30999bfbccf0175a1ba6f803ec5f6da","